%N A145698 Numbers x such that (x+37)^3 - x^3 is a square.
%H A145698 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (591,-591,1).
%F A145698 a(n+2) = 590*a(n+1) - a(n) + 10868.
%F A145698 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 12 2026: (Start)
%F A145698 a(n) = 37*A145700(n).
